      <li>Interfere with, overload, reverse engineer, scan, or attack the service.</li>
      <li>Upload malware or harmful code.</li>
      <li>Misrepresent your identity, credentials, services, location, availability, insurance, or pricing.</li>
      <li>Use TheraSaurus to route families to unavailable providers or unrelated businesses in a misleading way.</li>
      <li>Violate another person's privacy, intellectual property, or legal rights.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-8">
